videos.description: AJ Dillon runs through a wide open hole for a 45-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: BC's Dillon blasts through hole for long TD

videos.description: BC's Michael Walker fumbles a punt return, setting up Wake Forest in good field position.
videos.headline: Walker muffs punt deep in own territory

videos.description: Matt Colburn 2-yard touchdown run ties the game at 7.
videos.headline: Wake's Colburn plunges in for TD

videos.description: BC's Jeff Smith gets his back foot inbounds for a  27-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Smith drags back foot for great TD catch

videos.description: BC's punt team is a disaster as they drop the snap, get blocked and give up a Wake Forest touchdown.
videos.headline: Dropped snap leads to punt block, Wake TD

videos.description: Sam Hartman fires a 5-yard touchdown pass on a slant to Sage Surratt to put Wake up a score.
videos.headline: Surratt snatches slant for a TD

videos.description: BC's Anthony Brown tosses a deep pass to Kobay White for  35-yard touchdown.
videos.headline: Brown slings a deep pass White for TD

videos.description: Anthony Brown tosses floater to Tommy Sweeney for a 29-yard touchdown and a Boston College lead.
videos.headline: Brown lofts pass to Sweeney for score

videos.description: Anthony Brownt throws another deep ball to Ben Glines  for a 40-yard touchdown and a two-score lead.
videos.headline: Brown passes deep to Glines for big TD

videos.description: Sam Hartman finds Jack Freudenthal for a 5-yard touchdown pass late in Wake Forest's 41-34 loss to Boston College.
videos.headline: Hartman squeezes in tough TD pass
